# Process Flows

This folder contains business process flows, workflow diagrams, and system flow charts used for requirement analysis and QA testing activities.

## Included Documents

* External Organization Request Flow
* Sponsorship Module Process Flow
* Donation Module Process Flow
* User Registration Workflow

## Purpose

These workflow diagrams help in understanding business processes, approval hierarchies, user journeys, and system behavior, supporting test case design and validation activities.

## QA Activities Supported

* Requirement Analysis
* Test Scenario Design
* Workflow Validation
* Business Process Verification
* Requirement Traceability

## Tools Used

* Creately
* Draw.io
* Microsoft Visio
* Microsoft PowerPoint

